ces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d20d0ad5dd575425145ad8ec6d1a14efd89df8f","tid":106551,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人講下綠卡同美籍有咩分別? 平時聽人講專業, 投資移民係綠卡定美籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n綠卡 之後坐五年移民監 考個試宣誓就可以入藉"}]}